<bibRefCitation author="Cotterill" box="[189,441,445,472]" firstAuthor="Cotterill" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" pagination="165 - 179" refId="ref258547" refString="Cotterill F. P. D. 2002. A new species of horseshoe bat (Microchiroptera: Rhinolophidae) from southcentral Africa: with comments on its affinities and evolution, and the characterization of rhinolophid species. Journal of Zoology 256 (2): 165 - 179. https: // doi. org / 10.1017 / S 0952836902000201" type="journal article" year="2002">Cotterill (2002: 166)</bibRefCitation>
